Package: demoShiny
Title: Runs a 'Shiny' App as Demo or Shows an Overview of Available 'Shiny' Apps
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
  person("Sigbert", "Klinke", email="sigbert@hu-berlin.de", role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Mimics the demo functionality for 'Shiny' apps in a package. Apps stored the package subdirectory 'inst/shiny' can be called by demoShiny(topic).
Depends: shiny
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
